title: Who is one member that you're very sure will debut from I-Land? - Quora

response.answer_text: Key words: ‘One Member’ and ‘very sure’. Then that obviously goes to Heeseung. He has strong producer support and fanbase and he has nothing really you can complain about him except maybe he let’s others have their way too often but he’s great in everything and people recognize that. So ye Heeseung. I don’t need to be really detailed cause this is pretty much a no-brainer hahah. Btw if you don’t know who he is, he was meant to be debut from TXT but he was removed from the line up for unknown reasons. I-Land is his second chance to debut.
It’s just my guess;; but probably the team from Flicker, as well as Sunoo & Jay. Hanbin is possible too, seeing as he’s the popular wild card. I wish all of them could debut tho ;-;
